org.apache.ignite.ml.composition

Class BaggingModelTrainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.ml.trainers.DatasetTrainer<ModelsComposition,Double>
      • org.apache.ignite.ml.composition.BaggingModelTrainer

  • public abstract class BaggingModelTrainer
extends DatasetTrainer<ModelsComposition,Double>
    Abstract trainer implementing bagging logic. In each learning iteration the algorithm trains one model on subset of learning sample and subspace of features space. Each model is produced from same model-class [e.g. Decision Trees].
